WEBVTT

1
01:00:51.228 --> 01:00:54.493 
水手都称它黑海
Which Mariners called a sea of darkness

2
01:00:56.100 --> 01:01:00.400 
风中的红砂甚至吹到英国南岸
And red sand from this wind has flown as far as the south of England

3
01:01:00.738 --> 01:01:06.506 
落下的红雨让人误以为是鲜血
Producing showers so dense that they were mistaken for blood

4
01:01:06.810 --> 01:01:08.300 
胡说
Fiction!

5
01:01:09.580 --> 01:01:13.676 
南岸我有别墅，那里没有血雨
We have a house on that coast and it has never, never rained blood

6
01:01:13.784 --> 01:01:16.753 
千真万确，妳的朋友希罗多德
It is all true. Herodotus, your friend

7
01:01:16.854 --> 01:01:17.821 
我的朋友？
My friend

8
01:01:18.956 --> 01:01:20.787 
他全都记下来
He writes about it

9
01:01:21.592 --> 01:01:28.122 
他还记下叫塞蒙的热风
And he writes about a wind, the simoon

